c: 30
v: 9
t: "“Kodi sadayende pa dziko nkuona momwe adalili malekezero a omwe adaliko patsogolo pawo? Adali anyonga zambiri kuposa iwo. Adailima nthaka ndi kumangapo zomangamanga kuposa momwe iwo adamangirapo. Ndipo aneneri awo adawadzera ndi zizindikiro zoonekera (koma adawatsutsa, ndipo Allah adawawononga). Choncho Allah sadali owapondereza koma iwo ankadzipondereza okha"